==Threadless ==
[[File:Vrcthreadlesscatalogue.webp|thumb|Former catalogue of VRChat's Threadless store, from 2018 to May 2024.]]
On August 30, 2018, VRChat launched<ref>[https://medium.com/@vrchat/while-our-engineers-have-been-busy-hammering-away-at-the-app-gunter-has-been-working-on-something-1652c29d81a7 VRChat Store] on Medium; retrieved November 27, 2024.</ref> its first merchandise partnership, with Threadless. As of May 30, 2024, VRChat's store on Threadless was unpublished by VRChat, and replaced by their Merchandise Lab.